s://blog.naver.com/cookthedesign/223097358857\" target=\"_blank\">https://blog.naver.com/(주)파파스컴퍼니/223097358857</a></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f25b3710-dac4-4890-aca1-5fddb070a0dd\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-0b2ee4c8-e7b1-468d-a30f-37c7e2dac539\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><a class=\"se-link\" href=\"https://blog.naver.com/cookthedesign/223095451353\" target=\"_blank\">https://blog.naver.com/(주)파파스컴퍼니/223095451353</a></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-cefd0cf5-4938-40b7-a247-10b3bc56a11a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-4b29e1d1-4f39-44b2-918d-cc16c365136d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-wrappingParagraph se-l-inner-left\" id=\"SE-e00ff948-5488-43d7-989e-41a23d999b97\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-component-slot se-component-slot-float\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-a533a68e-ea61-4369-8ad6-88b6ed24b43d\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMzA1MTBfODAg/MDAxNjgzNjg4MjMyODI5.95gvnoLKw5a7X18Ts5fOIu_pQDBq4TsOdC5B1VXuDgEg.hBoUhpP5MVQsbnBCEhZXepeLHqs4HiavDCaz_r78pSwg.PNG.cookthedesign/s3.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"660\", \"originalHeight\" : \"238\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMzA1MTBfODAg/MDAxNjgzNjg4MjMyODI5.95gvnoLKw5a7X18Ts5fOIu_pQDBq4TsOdC5B1VXuDgEg.hBoUhpP5MVQsbnBCEhZXepeLHqs4HiavDCaz_r78pSwg.PNG.cookthedesign/s3.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component-slot\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3135bd0b-2c05-4d2b-9167-a69f3a6b4fa4\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-4e6a8739-db80-4a51-b45d-00f39e59bb74\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>인쇄비</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a8e2df4c-7b8c-494d-a8ed-861c7befed59\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-15a6d135-c0d7-4b8b-89e8-f87b379348b3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">인쇄비는 조금 복잡하게 견적이 진행됩니다. 종이와 관련된 통수를 알아야 하고 인쇄판 규격인 절수를 알아야 합니다. 자세한 설명을 드리는 것은 생략하겠습니다. 기본적인 설명만을 드립니다. 아주 간단한 리플렛부터 시작하겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7ea18758-b854-4158-81e9-699acf168ee7\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-4df140a2-4d9d-44e6-a288-615dae7f9a73\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-68352040-9520-4bc4-951f-f0d53c3fe6b8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-wrappingParagraph se-l-inner-left\" id=\"SE-2713becf-09fa-43c0-8046-77d4104be60c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-component-slot se-component-slot-float\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-77f897fa-e66b-4f7b-b406-dc1bb1e51194\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMzA1MTBfNzAg/MDAxNjgzNjg4NDQ4MTMz.NldSdKIdi1gqfYC3v84JglLNGackJ-Wo3V2yuhVOEaUg.SPkklbuCaVCbE8EBbrwQfeiZdorQZ1mFp2mXlo7ahIQg.PNG.cookthedesign/A.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"828\", \"originalHeight\" : \"237\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMzA1MTBfNzAg/MDAxNjgzNjg4NDQ4MTMz.NldSdKIdi1gqfYC3v84JglLNGackJ-Wo3V2yuhVOEaUg.SPkklbuCaVCbE8EBbrwQfeiZdorQZ1mFp2mXlo7ahIQg.PNG.cookthedesign/A.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component-slot\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0a8b0bab-0790-4d00-8d7e-ee8784915be1\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-25d93882-310b-42cf-bb40-b30fb9b09558\" style=\"color:#555555;\">노원구청에서 주민 홍보용으로 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-fb0b55ed-563d-405a-9aa0-d6d212415ecf\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#c2f4db;\">A3 단면칼라 포스터 10,000장</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-c93a8023-1c29-4777-b6b4-08d10d94b12a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">을 인쇄하려고 합니다. 이때 조달청 단가 기준 인쇄비는 어떻게 되나요?</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-wrappingParagraph se-l-inner-left\" id=\"SE-b7c3c4ab-93fc-433f-89d5-c52d65350765\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-component-slot se-component-slot-float\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-9db532a2-f005-47c0-872b-f9f47c601596\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMzA1MTBfMTcx/MDAxNjgzNjg4NDgwMTY5.aAw2kBun5nMbj8MurAK6BPYfvC08u6BYq9MVCif-ZdQg.0_4oWeVshlLBLSe8sjfnpJ3yGpjCq1YXEvZXJhaZx-Ug.PNG.cookthedesign/Q.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"828\", \"originalHeight\" : \"238\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMzA1MTBfMTcx/MDAxNjgzNjg4NDgwMTY5.aAw2kBun5nMbj8MurAK6BPYfvC08u6BYq9MVCif-ZdQg.0_4oWeVshlLBLSe8sjfnpJ3yGpjCq1YXEvZXJhaZx-Ug.PNG.cookthedesign/Q.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component-slot\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-db0aff2e-44bd-419d-98a7-6a161646bccf\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-967cfff7-37b6-4cac-9ff2-cb9ef105c118\" style=\"color:#555555;\">일단 정답은 23,000원입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-cef37cfe-1459-4544-8068-64a925c2b263\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-58ff70f5-fde3-436f-a287-80157bfd4c46\" style=\"color:#555555;\">인쇄비를 계산할 때는 기본적으로 절수와 장수가 필요합니다. 어떤 사이즈로 얼마나 찍을 건지입니다. 디지털인쇄의 경우는 A4 그대로 인쇄를 찍고 그 장수만큼 단가를 적용하겠지만 옵셋인쇄의 경우는 그 내용이 다릅니다. 일단 인쇄사이즈에 대해 궁금하시다면 다음 글을 참고해 주시기 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b85103a9-f16d-428b-8138-c256c952463d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-504a2a2d-c299-4cf2-aa1e-1c7d62083e40\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><a class=\"se-link\" href=\"https://blog.naver.com/cookthedesign/222895077740\" target=\"_blank\">https://blog.naver.com/(주)파파스컴퍼니/222895077740</a></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-9582d556-6a4d-4966-b474-a7bc789c6cab\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f5a00ec5-93eb-46c4-85dd-8016cfed9300\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-3e413511-9c95-4656-9d7e-ff860b435d10\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5e80dfd8-aafa-41ac-8935-3f335fcb9bbc\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-f8c3b808-160a-4e61-a90e-533ba2641b18\" style=\"color:#555555;\">국 2절 인쇄기에는 A3 사이즈 인쇄물이 2개 앉혀집니다. 이런 이유로 정이 단위인 1R을 국전 인쇄하면 500장 * 4 = 2,000장이 나옵니다. 우리가 지라시를 인쇄할 때 A4 기본 매수가 4,000장인 이유사 절수와 종이 기본 단위 500장의 상관관계 때문입니다. A4의 2배인 A3는 1R을 인쇄하면 2,000장이 기본입니다. 그렇기에 10,000장 포스터라면 5R이 인쇄되는 겁니다. 5R이면 A3 포스터 10,000장이 인쇄되는 식입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-464d1672-4856-4007-8384-1e967c3dca40\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-257d5e92-8c29-4f91-8e22-a5fefcd65f25\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-da35978e-1f1d-4c33-bf72-f702cfc5e89a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-208208c1-4c7b-45d6-9fb0-3dd9a744cd7a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">그러면 국 2절 인쇄에서 통수는 얼마일까요? 국 2절 1R의 통수는 당연히 1,000장입니다. 이유는 국전 500장이 기본 1R의 총 통수라면 그 1/2인 국 2절 인쇄 시에는 2배로 통수가 증가합니다. 국전은 반으로 잘라 인쇄하기 때문에 통수는 2배가 증가하는 원리입니다. 그러면 10,000장을 국 2절로 인쇄하면 통수는 5,000장입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d0784362-ebf8-467c-bb97-7dc7a00403f5\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:523px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-d0784362-ebf8-467c-bb97-7dc7a00403f5\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMzA1MTBfOTMg/MDAxNjgzNjk4MjIxMTY1.S88ywCEPff-943sLWgIxKAwrhWz4azNSYwyNh-Dny60g.C_igrIkH5gQ_cXX_vbdx6wH3rFIeeiBMQ_PgrBkzshog.PNG.cookthedesign/image.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"523\", \"originalHeight\" : \"37\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMzA1MTBfOTMg/MDAxNjgzNjk4MjIxMTY1.S88ywCEPff-943sLWgIxKAwrhWz4azNSYwyNh-Dny60g.C_igrIkH5gQ_cXX_vbdx6wH3rFIeeiBMQ_PgrBkzshog.PNG.cookthedesign/image.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-224b6b20-4de5-4700-8fc1-31c0a85ef59f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:111px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-224b6b20-4de5-4700-8fc1-31c0a85ef59f\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMzA1MTBfMTQ1/MDAxNjgzNjk4MjYyNDQz.vgK76ia1GRdlSoLYRaWLso82SV0pmkkY1BRDVReYt20g.RZ2yzzOp7V-YfcwkvkURG9hVMObUgoHVEE6hkCrQKsQg.PNG.cookthedesign/image.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"111\", \"originalHeight\" : \"306\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMzA1MTBfMTQ1/MDAxNjgzNjk4MjYyNDQz.vgK76ia1GRdlSoLYRaWLso82SV0pmkkY1BRDVReYt20g.RZ2yzzOp7V-YfcwkvkURG9hVMObUgoHVEE6hkCrQKsQg.PNG.cookthedesign/image.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6b36af3b-59a0-4600-8003-241070670863\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8ccd7b41-6625-482f-8b88-02cceeeab3fe\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-3b8b5ed4-874f-4354-b97b-9fa384be3fb5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">옵셋인쇄료에서 5,000통의 4도 인쇄가 36.16원입니다. 그러므로 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-b4465561-a855-4d46-8bfa-0db6e9b3f851\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#c2f4db;\"><b>36.16 * 5,000 = 180,800원으로 견적금이 책정</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-83aa9f05-ca1d-4259-9654-2523d8204675\" style=\"color:#555555;\">됩니다. 그리고 위의 표는 46 2절 기준으로 명시되어 있습니다. 국 사이즈인 경우 가감이 적용됩니다. 그 부율은 아래 주에 나옵니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-732cff9e-fd18-4dfc-89c2-da3a85bf4b55\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-44883412-6bf1-42da-ad1e-75bce4d7a246\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-table se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b5411222-9747-4fb8-b417-2e2b77d65980\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-table se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"width: 72%;\">\n<div class=\"se-table-container\">\n<table class=\"se-table-content\" style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1px 0px 0px 1px; border-color: #d2d2d2;\">\n<tbody><tr class=\"se-tr\"><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 100.0%; height: 26.0px; border-style: solid; border-width: 0px 1px 1px 0px; border-color: #d2d2d2; \">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-87b08117-10af-44ea-9771-67bb4b72da9c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-nanumsquare se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-e60d7465-ece1-4cfa-9583-27791bfec7fa\" style=\"color:#000000;\">1) 1</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-nanumsquare se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-953547e6-0f35-4fab-83b4-1330a857d8f1\" style=\"color:#000000;\">50g／m2  이상의 후지 또는 50g／m2  이하의 박엽지로 인쇄할 경우에는 30%를 가산한다.</span></p></div>\n</td></tr><tr class=\"se-tr\"><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 100.0%; height: 26.0px; border-style: solid; border-width: 0px 1px 1px 0px; border-color: #d2d2d2; \">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-df820e73-b8e4-4493-a2b2-5ccca581e175\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-nanumsquare se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-04960892-1354-498f-9290-d382a920ae79\" style=\"color:#000000;\">2) 원색인쇄는 20%를 가산한다.</span></p></div>\n</td></tr><tr class=\"se-tr\"><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 100.0%; height: 26.0px; border-style: solid; border-width: 0px 1px 1px 0px; border-color: #d2d2d2; \">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-f9acdd45-cfca-4388-87b0-6acb86aa73b6\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-nanumsquare se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-7cbb3d32-6756-4e80-bcc4-00befdebc797\" style=\"color:#000000;\">3) 금분, 은분,펄(빠루), 특수별색인쇄는 100%를 가산한다.</span></p></div>\n</td></tr><tr class=\"se-tr\"><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 100.0%; height: 26.0px; border-style: solid; border-width: 0px 1px 1px 0px; border-color: #d2d2d2; \">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-a7ef4025-488a-41d6-abe5-efe465fea4db\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-nanumsquare se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-1c0d6151-30c3-4e55-8988-d83be1edea8a\" style=\"color:#000000;\">4) 전면 베다인쇄는 60%를 가산한다.</span></p></div>\n</td></tr><tr class=\"se-tr\"><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 100.0%; height: 26.0px; border-style: solid; border-width: 0px 1px 1px 0px; border-color: #d2d2d2; \">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-0b4835d1-e00c-4243-8408-2986b094afac\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-nanumsquare se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-8b0b8ab5-8f1b-40fa-a9a1-dd224c3fb183\" style=\"color:#000000;\">5) 국판계열로 인쇄할 경우 국배판은 20%, 국판은 33%를 감산한다.</span></p></div>\n</td></tr><tr class=\"se-tr\"><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 100.0%; height: 26.0px; border-style: solid; border-width: 0px 1px 1px 0px; border-color: #d2d2d2; \">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-9aa0443a-19a5-44a9-ae0a-20023daf1b51\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-nanumsquare se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-78463935-bc9a-4e6c-bb97-44c74d55316f\" style=\"color:#000000;\">6) 1,000통 미만은 1,000통으로 계산한다.</span></p></div>\n</td></tr><tr class=\"se-tr\"><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 100.0%; height: 26.0px; border-style: solid; border-width: 0px 1px 1px 0px; border-color: #d2d2d2; \">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-81c11f20-9a1b-4599-abea-2ca06898d45e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-nanumsquare se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-ed0f618b-2a8b-4994-a5b8-1c6b14dacd61\" style=\"color:#000000;\">7) 4× 6전지 단일 인쇄물로 4도 인쇄시 70연 이상인 경우에는 다음과 같이 기본인쇄 요금에서 일정비율을 감산한다.</span></p></div>\n</td></tr><tr class=\"se-tr\"><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 100.0%; height: 26.0px; border-style: solid; border-width: 0px 1px 1px 0px; border-color: #d2d2d2; \">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-f7a1009a-a4c1-427c-b01d-d877886e3b3f\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-nanumsquare se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-31166f73-452a-4dd2-8f12-30007ee58e8b\" style=\"color:#000000;\">가) 4× 6전지 70연 이상 100연 미만 : 3% </span></p></div>\n</td></tr><tr class=\"se-tr\"><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 100.0%; height: 26.0px; border-style: solid; border-width: 0px 1px 1px 0px; border-color: #d2d2d2; \">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-f3694f31-fb34-4b5c-995b-3ebade9dc572\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-nanumsquare se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-35b3446b-785d-4fc4-9651-37a25f346a6b\" style=\"color:#000000;\">나) 4× 6전지 100연 이상 150연 미만 : 5%</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-nanumsquare se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-59da9581-2cdf-439d-8edc-c867cf7e5a66\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span></p></div>\n</td></tr><tr class=\"se-tr\"><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 100.0%; height: 26.0px; border-style: solid; border-width: 0px 1px 1px 0px; border-color: #d2d2d2; \">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-09259e0c-c544-45f3-a23f-1ee9ed62db51\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-nanumsquare se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-3d3c3cfb-6292-41cb-a019-bb09c00c85f2\" style=\"color:#000000;\">다) 4× 6전지 150연 이상 200연 미만 : 6% </span></p></div>\n</td></tr><tr class=\"se-tr\"><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 100.0%; height: 26.0px; border-style: solid; border-width: 0px 1px 1px 0px; border-color: #d2d2d2; \">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-f61464e0-49fd-42b1-ae50-38e4abd4982a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-nanumsquare se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-088c847d-5c11-4189-9231-201836e8e0fb\" style=\"color:#000000;\">라) 4× 6전지 200연 이상  : 7%</span></p></div>\n</td></tr><tr class=\"se-tr\"><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 100.0%; height: 26.0px; border-style: solid; border-width: 0px 1px 1px 0px; border-color: #d2d2d2; \">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9aea38d5-aabe-43f6-bb6e-aebe56449af1\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-nanumsquare se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-ec88ca86-4b42-48e5-a71c-4a33b0862bed\" style=\"color:#000000;\">8) 3절인쇄는 2절인쇄의 67% 요금을 계산한다.</span></p></div>\n</td></tr><tr class=\"se-tr\"><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 100.0%; height: 26.0px; border-style: solid; border-width: 0px 1px 1px 0px; border-color: #d2d2d2; \">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2b1631f9-3bc0-4847-b197-bc128f487a30\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-nanumsquare se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-6d50567a-c07f-45b0-9c26-6a8446238ecf\" style=\"color:#000000;\">9) 전지는 2절인쇄의 100% 가산, 4절은 50% 감산한다</span></p></div>\n</td></tr></tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-11c1e7fe-19c2-4c4c-b826-72f75ac2a51f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-87909acc-2715-4c30-a519-d9329ff1881f\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-b6fd3116-4879-46ca-84c9-f9f2878a5130\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이 주의 5번을 보면 국배판과 국판의 가감을 계산합니다. 국배판은 국전, 국판은 국 2절로 이해해 주세요. 그러면 앞에서 계산되어 단가의 33%를 감산합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-70a578a4-dd20-43ef-94ea-60969af2fa5a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-7dda0440-d637-4793-ab1f-636051bba59a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8563b4b3-b19c-4528-a5a0-25ff730295ab\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-199d3bbb-1c0f-4549-8ab2-72a88b7d64a0\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#c2f4db;\"><b> 180,800원 *.67 = 121,136원입니다. 최종 견적가는 121,136원입니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-fac899df-7d78-442f-88c7-b9ac33a825e1\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-c9a2bf81-5607-4aa4-96f4-3c08de3ee188\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0891caab-f986-4bd6-8456-9facbdcb2438\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-38299f94-f3bc-4155-8da2-d82e87f54e99\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이를 일반적인 인쇄계산단가로 나타내보면 단면/5R을 국 2절 기계로 인쇄했을 때 1R 당 단가를 6,057원 계산하다는 뜻입니다. 5R 인쇄비 6,000원이면 괜찮은 단가라고 생각됩니다.~ 또 베다 인쇄와 종이에 따른 추가 비용을 청구해 계산할 수 있어 조달청 단가는 살아 있다고 느껴집니다.~</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ae7727c3-89c6-4ce7-8389-46f71dee4f44\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-wrappingParagraph se-l-inner-left\" id=\"SE-ffc6fc80-ecbd-4642-b8b5-3154b0675e6c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-component-slot se-component-slot-float\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-70617c89-eabd-49fc-9a29-73924e67afc3\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMzA1MTBfMjY2/MDAxNjgzNjk5NDc5MTM3.SP2C9avs5c44YRffNnLewyyy-CqxWyhgS-8ASsf8v-Ig.Ki0nbWUdp1rMZg1Q8b0m8xzDz0TzeWKF35j7d0JDvzAg.PNG.cookthedesign/s4.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"660\", \"originalHeight\" : \"237\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMzA1MTBfMjY2/MDAxNjgzNjk5NDc5MTM3.SP2C9avs5c44YRffNnLewyyy-CqxWyhgS-8ASsf8v-Ig.Ki0nbWUdp1rMZg1Q8b0m8xzDz0TzeWKF35j7d0JDvzAg.PNG.cookthedesign/s4.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component-slot\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3a482c71-104f-4466-9a09-33376c3aa1ae\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-b6a01b37-0a70-4210-8c93-ff91367304e7\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>책자제본료</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-34a974c3-dc8a-49be-8b9d-ba0e4d652419\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-d140e978-dbb9-47b2-a25c-62c654b85175\" style=\"color:#555555;\">제본 비용은 크게 3가지 밖에 없습니다. 거의 중철 제본은 안 하는지 모르지만 일단 단가표에서는 발견하지 못했습니다. 물론 시중가격이나 기타 항목을 정의한 부분이 있기는 하지만 일단 기본적인 제본 방식인 중철 제본에 대한 설명이나 단가는 없었습니다. 제본에 대한 방식과 기타 사항이 궁금하신 분은 다음 글을 참고하고 돌아와 주세요.~</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-817ac3b6-f430-4748-ae04-7213e0241b4a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-a5058c01-a8e1-4558-bb14-a43076439e67\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><a class=\"se-link\" href=\"https://blog.naver.com/cookthedesign/222898545921\" target=\"_blank\">https://blog.naver.com/(주)파파스컴퍼니/222898545921</a></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-table se-l-default\" id=\"SE-670802f7-6f35-4bbb-b128-cd1b68835f4f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-table se-l-default se-section-align-\" style