ph se-text-paragraph-align-right\" id=\"SE-b8031883-8b85-4225-8673-317c59b2ae86\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-84a7a4a7-7de4-4e0a-b021-e949c84e3b0d\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b>1.738 </b></span></p></div>\n</td></tr><tr class=\"se-tr\"><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 25.0%; height: 26.0px; border-style: solid; border-width: 0px 1px 1px 0px; border-color: #d2d2d2; background-color: #F2F2F2;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-11d87b06-8e43-4e5a-a03c-24b6d25f2d3a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-3298aef8-89ac-4b35-beac-05d40c46accd\" style=\"color:#000000;\">크라운판(18절)</span></p></div>\n</td><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 25.0%; height: 26.0px; border-style: solid; border-width: 0px 1px 1px 0px; border-color: #d2d2d2; background-color: #ffff00;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-fb7128f5-ff17-42ad-b9c1-83fdc39bf3c7\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-242c58c3-4326-4ad7-8495-875f3b4b2c93\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b>1.092 </b></span></p></div>\n</td><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 25.0%; height: 26.0px; border-style: solid; border-width: 0px 1px 1px 0px; border-color: #d2d2d2; background-color: #ffff00;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-right\" id=\"SE-5162e8ea-9f70-4847-912c-a9c782a69617\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-8b4a5d53-741f-49a5-a31b-bcead1079d40\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b>1.319 </b></span></p></div>\n</td><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 25.0%; height: 26.0px; border-style: solid; border-width: 0px 1px 1px 0px; border-color: #d2d2d2; background-color: #ffff00;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-right\" id=\"SE-80cea7e9-7713-49ea-a8b6-a8de8092b306\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-13b8acfc-9b87-4ac9-8a3f-e7959e0e0486\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b>1.876 </b></span></p></div>\n</td></tr></tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-97d07b82-c4d1-4ee1-b321-2a2efe62dce3\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-97a63ca2-dfa1-45ba-abba-f53e7c63e86a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-18acf76b-71a0-44be-bb0e-0257f5c2b9c9\" style=\"color:#555555;\">제가 검토하면서 제일 이해가 안 되는 단가가 제본료입니다. 아무리 계산해도 현실과 조금 달라서 놀랐습니다. 만약 예를 들어 A4 카탈로그 100페이지 1,000부를 무선제본으로 계산하면 다음과 같습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-53eb7350-e4bc-429c-9beb-aef8d7b56ca1\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-f1d8ce7b-8db9-4952-a81e-4f001451e802\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-72d95088-1b56-4c15-88dc-ba9a8a6f8ac9\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-75725ce9-891b-4bd1-aeee-6f56fc3ed738\" style=\"color:#555555;\">무사무선철 : </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-d3a5cd3b-a5fd-459e-8302-8b7343d8a520\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#c2f4db;\"><b>2.116원 * 100p * 1,000부 = 211,600원</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-f492281b-2ea8-45cf-bbf7-d65b930763f0\" style=\"color:#555555;\">입니다. 이 금액이 합리적인지는 일단 각자 점검해 보시기 바랍니다.~ 하지만 페이지 수가 많고 부수가 많으면 단가는 점점 개선되는 것으로 나옵니다. 이 부분은 조금 수량에 대한 단가 반영이 안된 것으로 보입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine 